00:10:07.000 --> 00:10:23.000
 I would note that in the above examples, the else and the if in C are two language constructs that are just being used idiomatically to construct a multi-way branch or else if pattern with indentation that captures the idiom.

00:10:23.000 --> 00:10:37.000
