00:40:46.800 --> 00:40:49.200
 And then close curly brace to end the loop.

00:40:49.200 --> 00:40:52.960
 And if I wanted to skip blanks and new lines, I could use both break and

00:40:52.960 --> 00:40:57.680
 continue, further angering the structured programming purists.

00:40:57.680 --> 00:41:01.040
 Int, C semicolon.

00:41:01.040 --> 00:41:04.560
 While open parenthesis one, close parenthesis, open curly brace,

00:41:04.560 --> 00:41:09.240
