00:41:26.520 --> 00:41:32.360
 I use this middle tested approach because usually the data I am processing is coming

00:41:32.360 --> 00:41:34.520
 from a more complex source than the keyboard.

00:41:34.520 --> 00:41:39.000
 And I don't want a function with two to three parameters stuck inside of a side

00:41:39.000 --> 00:41:42.000
