00:41:58.320 --> 00:42:01.240
 Even Kernigan and Ritchie point out its benefits above.

00:42:01.240 --> 00:42:07.600
 And with that, I have now triggered endless coffee shop conversations

00:42:07.600 --> 00:42:10.680
