00:43:02.920 --> 00:43:04.000
 do some stuff.

00:43:04.000 --> 00:43:09.720
 If, open parenthesis, disaster, close parenthesis, go to, error, semi-colon,

00:43:09.720 --> 00:43:14.400
 close curly brace, dot, dot, dot, dot, dot, and then error, colon, and

00:43:14.400 --> 00:43:16.000
 then clean up the mess.

00:43:16.000 --> 00:43:20.320
 This organization is handy if the error handling code is non-trivial and

00:43:20.320 --> 00:43:22.720
 if errors can occur in several places.

00:43:22.720 --> 00:43:26.960
 A label has the same form as a variable name and is followed by a colon.

00:43:26.960 --> 00:43:31.600
 It can be attached to any statement in the same function as the go to.

